EN: Having good communication skills is necessary to promote interpersonal relationships.

ZH: 培养自律能力是必需的，可以提升自我管理能力。
EN: Cultivating self-discipline is essential for improving self-management skills.

ZH: 社会经验是必需的，可以帮助人们更好地融入社会。
EN: Social experience is necessary to help people better integrate into society.

ZH: 忠诚和信任是建立人际关系的必需条件。
EN: Loyalty and trust are essential prerequisites for building relationships.

ZH: 在生活中学会感恩是必需的，可以让人更加幸福。
EN: Learning gratitude in life is necessary to make people happier.
